HEADWORD: Scansion
<hw>Scan"sion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>scansio</ets>, fr. <ets>scandere</ets>, <ets>scansum</ets>, to
climb. See <er>Scan</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Pros.)</fld> <def>The act of
